# This file is used to ensure the directory is tracked by Git.
# You can replace the SVG placeholder files in this directory with your actual avatar images.
# Naming convention: avatar_AGE_SEX_SKIN.svg
# AGE: child, teen, adult, senior
# SEX: male, female, neutral
# SKIN: light, medium-light, medium, medium-dark, dark
# Example: avatar_adult_female_medium.svg
